Male. 21. Head, dorsal view; 22. antenna, lateral view; 23. epandrium, posterior view; 24. epandrium, lateral view; 25. hypandrium and phallic complex, ventral view. Scale bar of 21 = 0.50 mm, 22 = 0.33 mm, 23–24 = 0.25 mm, 25 = 0.22 mm.
</paragraph>
